Interface Monitoring

  • All Superinterfaces:

    MonitoringImpl

    public interface Monitoring
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Monitoring'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Thread Names
    • Shared Resources
    • Analysis Context
